{"tid":37669,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"［突發］P Chan 再發帖解釋：刪學生問題再轉發","createTime":"2016-12-13T13:03:00.000Z","updateTime":"2016-12-13T13:10:15.000Z","uid":53173,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"6a907d533931f33ef9da66c9b5602d168b6986f6","tid":37669,"uid":53173,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-13T13:03:00.000Z","msg":"P Chan再發帖解釋：刪學生問題再轉發<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2016/12/13/210101_e9c10ac14b08d4dc922e37da6f64a51d.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2016%2F12%2F13%2F210101_e9c10ac14b08d4dc922e37da6f64a51d.jpg&h=d5a32e3e&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2016/12/13/210102_29a73a5faf924e3c298d030250f26dbc.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2016%2F12%2F13%2F210102_29a73a5faf924e3c298d030250f26dbc.jpg&h=fdef400d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n網上發酵逾日，P Chan在今日凌晨時分再貼上手機WhatsApp截圖，圖中的訊息內容跟早前的訊息差不多，但內容較詳細，而且對方還有詢問問題。P Chan在帖文中指出新上載的截圖是原文，因為想刪掉學生私人問題再轉發其他朋友，所以才會用「精簡」版訊息出帖。他又斥責「打手」大造文章，希望網上打手停止抹黑，更表示「教學二十多年，一向頂天立地，堅守原則及操守，但無良的導師仍然請大量打手抹黑及攻撃我，這是我最感到悲哀！」<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.hk01.com/熱話/59795/補習天王fb惹公關災難-學生鼓勵訊息遭網民質疑造假\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.hk01.com%2F%E7%86%B1%E8%A9%B1%2F59795%2F%E8%A3%9C%E7%BF%92%E5%A4%A9%E7%8E%8Bfb%E6%83%B9%E5%85%AC%E9%97%9C%E7%81%BD%E9%9B%A3-%E5%AD%B8%E7%94%9F%E9%BC%93%E5%8B%B5%E8%A8%8A%E6%81%AF%E9%81%AD%E7%B6%B2%E6%B0%91%E8%B3%AA%E7%96%91%E9%80%A0%E5%81%87&d=n512dPcxF4iVd0ZnK%2Fi65IscwJTI%2BQouKF8MUrnyvY0%3D&h=fe54617b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://www.hk01.com/熱話/59795/補習天王fb惹公關災難-學生鼓勵訊息遭網民質疑造假</a>"},{"pid":"8659cb2548684102605d515abeb9bd12bd7d49f3","tid":37669,"uid":90,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-13T13:04:45.000Z","msg":"Ok,我信佢"},{"pid":"24c9c00ec133270d5bb34cd959cad479822567a5","tid":37669,"uid":10338,"like":0,"dislike